  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>Choice of comfortable bedrooms all with bath (with shower attachment), separate WC, flat screen TV, high speed internet access and a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Standard rooms</strong>: sleep 2</p>
<p><strong>Twin Superior rooms</strong>: sleep 2 with views of the pistes</p>
<p><strong>Triple rooms</strong>: sleep 3 with 3 single beds</p>
<p><strong>Quad rooms</strong>: sleep 4 with twin beds and bunk beds.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>All rooms have twin beds which can be made up as doubles, let us know if you prefer this. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
